'''Tysys Ryx''' was a [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] who managed pit fighters in the quasi-legal "[[blood arena]]" circuit. At one point in his career he owned the [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]] [[Huggtar]], an excellent fighter, until his contract was bought by [[Zhen Mirat]].

